# SEV-1 regression guard: with no prior panes, http.new used to leave
# Layout::Empty. Confirm the pane actually draws.
# The three-panel layout (Request/Response/AI) removed the [Edit][Response]
# tab strip — assertions updated to check elements that ARE in the new
# layout (method chip, response section header, ai section header).

command http.new

expect screen contains "GET"
expect screen contains "response"
expect screen contains "ai"
expect pane "request"
